@NODE News "sort v1.80 Documentation - What's new"
What's new in this version?

- an option has been added that appends the lines to the outfile
  if this already exists @{" info " link Ä}

- using the u option you can erase lines which are completely in
  another line. @{" info " link U}

- the y|Y option allows to set the sorting column after a search pattern.
  this option works together with -i|I option. @{" info " link Y}

- the Z option allows sorting binary (!) files. Requirement is a constant
  length of data record. @{" info " link Z}

@{" Contents " link MAIN}
@ENDNODE

